1、Error: Cannot find module @ionic\app-scripts'
    npm install @ionic/app-scripts@latest --save-dev
    
2、ionic build android (或cordova build android)
    报错：Error: Could not find an installed version of Gradle either in Android Studio,
    or on your system to install the gradle wrapper. Please include gradle
    in your path, or install Android Studio
    
    1、手动下载gradle
        gradle-x.x-bin.zip （x.x代表版本） 
        根据需要下载某一版本 
        地址： 
        (https://services.gradle.org/distributions)

     2、添加环境变量
         PATH=C:\Program Files\gradle-x.x\bin
        
     3、关闭cmd或powershell窗口
     4、重新打开，输入gradle -v，查看gradle安装成功与否
     5、重新build
